<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 12:28:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>消息人士称，印度塔塔工厂火灾后，苹果可能需要转向中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-may-need-turn-china-after-indian-tata-plant-fire-sources-say-2024-10-01/</link><description>一位行业观察家和消息人士称，塔塔集团位于印度南部的苹果 iPhone 零部件工厂发生火灾造成的大面积损失可能会在节日销售激增之前阻碍生产，迫使这家美国公司的供应商从中国或其他地方安排关键零部件。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 11:36:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-may-need-turn-china-after-indian-tata-plant-fire-sources-say-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>据天空电视台报道，英国和中国正在就恢复经济讨论进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/uk-china-talks-about-resuming-economy-discussions-sky-reports-2024-10-01/</link><description>据天空新闻周二报道，英国财政部官员和中国财政部官员正在详细讨论举行 2019 年以来首次高级财政部官员高级别会议。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 11:33:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/uk-china-talks-about-resuming-economy-discussions-sky-reports-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>美国议员要求墨西哥候任总统解决中国汽车问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-lawmakers-ask-mexican-president-elect-address-chinese-vehicle-concerns-2024-10-01/</link><description>周二，美国国会约 20 名民主党人敦促墨西哥当选总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆解决中国汽车制造商在墨西哥生产的联网汽车带来的国家安全问题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 11:06:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-lawmakers-ask-mexican-president-elect-address-chinese-vehicle-concerns-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>北约新任主席表示，中国对俄罗斯的支持应该产生影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-support-russia-should-have-implications-new-nato-chief-says-2024-10-01/</link><description>北约新任秘书长马克·吕特周二表示，中国已成为俄罗斯乌克兰战争的决定性推动者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 10:25:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-support-russia-should-have-implications-new-nato-chief-says-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：第四季度股市创历史新高，欧元通胀低于预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-01/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 10:08:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>肖尔茨表示，德国的目标是成为量子技术的世界领先者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/germany-aims-be-world-leader-quantum-technologies-says-scholz-2024-10-01/</link><description>德国总理奥拉夫·肖尔茨 (Olaf Scholz) 誓言支持量子技术的发展，他在周二 IBM 数据中心的启用仪式上表示，对该领域的投资对于欧洲最大经济体的未来至关重要。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 10:04:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/germany-aims-be-world-leader-quantum-technologies-says-scholz-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>检察官称中国女子因涉嫌间谍活动在德国被捕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/chinese-woman-arrested-germany-suspicion-espionage-prosecutor-says-2024-10-01/</link><description>德国总检察长周二在一份声明中表示，一名中国女子因涉嫌外国特工活动和传递有关武器交付的信息而在德国莱比锡市被捕。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 09:34:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/chinese-woman-arrested-germany-suspicion-espionage-prosecutor-says-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>印度陆军参谋长表示，印度和中国解决边界对峙的选择</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/options-india-china-resolve-border-stand-off-indian-army-chief-says-2024-10-01/</link><description>印度陆军参谋长周二表示，印度和中国外交官之间的会谈为亚洲竞争对手解决喜马拉雅边境冲突提供了选择。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 08:15:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/options-india-china-resolve-border-stand-off-indian-army-chief-says-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>日本绝大多数男性内阁再次凸显性别差距</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japans-overwhelmingly-male-cabinet-underlines-gender-gap-again-2024-10-01/</link><description>日本新首相周二只任命了两名女性加入其 20 名内阁成员，低于之前的五名女性，人权组织表示，这代表东京在推动提高女性政治代表性方面的“倒退”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 08:02:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japans-overwhelmingly-male-cabinet-underlines-gender-gap-again-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>新华社报道，中美将就经贸问题举行会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-us-hold-talks-economic-trade-issues-xinhua-reports-2024-10-01/</link><description>中国官方媒体新华社周二援引知情人士的话报道称，中国商务部部长王文涛将在不久的将来与美国商务部部长就经贸关系举行通话。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 07:02:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-us-hold-talks-economic-trade-issues-xinhua-reports-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>Nio 与 Monolith 合作进行实时人工智能电动汽车电池测试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/nio-partners-with-monolith-real-time-ai-ev-battery-testing-2024-10-01/</link><description>蔚来汽车周二表示，该公司正在与英国人工智能软件初创公司 Monolith 合作，利用这家中国电动汽车制造商在欧洲的电池更换服务来实时测试和改进电动汽车电池组。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 06:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/nio-partners-with-monolith-real-time-ai-ev-battery-testing-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体报道，中国军队在南海部分地区进行巡逻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-conducts-patrols-parts-south-china-sea-state-media-2024-10-01/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，中国军队周一至周二在南海部分地区进行了战备巡逻，这是周末在该地区罕见的军事演习和演习的延伸。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 04:49:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-conducts-patrols-parts-south-china-sea-state-media-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>媒体报道，越南渔船在有争议的南海岛屿附近遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-fishing-boat-attacked-near-contested-south-china-sea-islands-media-2024-10-01/</link><description>据官方媒体周一晚间报道，至少 10 名越南渔民在中国和越南均声称拥有主权的西沙群岛附近捕鱼时遭到外国船只袭击，造成至少 10 名越南渔民受伤。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 03:01:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-fishing-boat-attacked-near-contested-south-china-sea-islands-media-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>如果中国克服真菌担忧，澳大利亚可能成为油菜籽贸易赢家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/australia-could-be-canola-trade-winner-if-china-gets-over-fungus-worries-2024-10-01/</link><description>如果中国对加拿大进口的油籽征收关税，澳大利亚可能会成为全球油菜籽贸易流向转变的赢家，但北京方面需要克服他们对真菌的担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 02:44:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/australia-could-be-canola-trade-winner-if-china-gets-over-fungus-worries-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>台湾警告强台风“克拉通”带来的风暴潮并动员军队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/troops-mobilised-taiwan-warns-storm-surge-powerful-typhoon-krathon-2024-10-01/</link><description>周二，强大的台风“克拉通”逼近人口稠密的西南海岸，台湾动员了近 4 万名士兵，随时待命，准备应对风暴潮。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 02:28:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/troops-mobilised-taiwan-warns-storm-surge-powerful-typhoon-krathon-2024-10-01/</guid></item></channel></rss>